-- MUFG: Not decided on Morgan Stanley per share price
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2008 9:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/22/us-financial-morgan-stanley-mufg-price-idUSTFA00303420080922

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group, Japan's largest bank, said it is still carrying out due diligence on Morgan Stanley and has not yet decided on a per share price for its stake acquisition. 

 Jiji news agency reported earlier that MUFG had estimated it could pay $31 for each Morgan Stanley share, and a total of 900 billion yen ($8.49 billion) for the stake. A MUFG spokesman said it had not yet decided on such details. (Reporting by  Nathan Layne  and  Junko Fujita ; editing by Sue Thomas)